headline: Has Williams Companies Run Ahead of Its Value After Recent LNG Expansion Momentum?
summary: If you are holding Williams Companies or thinking about adding it to your portfolio, you have good reason to pause and take stock (pun intended). In a market where energy infrastructure names can sometimes fly under the radar, Williams has quietly delivered robust long-term returns. Just look at the past five years: up more than 319.7%, easily outpacing many peers and benchmarks. Even over the last three years, the stock is up a remarkable 144.2%.
